{"tid":854519,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"美國隊長迷腦內多達八粒瘤 Chris Evans拍片鼓勵小Fans","createTime":"2018-10-09T11:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T09:40:47.000Z","uid":212399,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd2e0206b3050107ce349cdac00d9fe90ec905b","tid":854519,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181009/large/1539081541_02a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F1539081541_02a0.jpg&h=f925cb5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181009/large/1539081541_f570.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F1539081541_f570.jpg&h=8abaffb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8歲嘅AJ腦入面有8粒瘤（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181009/large/1539081541_7353.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F1539081541_7353.jpg&h=9eeda27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基斯伊雲斯知道之後即刻拍片鼓勵小fans（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181009/large/1539081547_98e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F1539081547_98e6.jpg&h=ae2ce240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基斯話自己只係演英雄，但對方就係真英雄（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181009/large/1539081547_beae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F1539081547_beae.jpg&h=3f1c10f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAJ收到片之後好開心咁拍片回應（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n「美國隊長」基斯伊雲斯（Chris Evans）自2011年開始演美國隊長，多年來形象深入民心，廣受fans歡迎，而佢於3月受訪時已證實演完《復仇者聯盟4》就會唔再演美國隊長。（新聞連結：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2E6mnBf￼&nbsp;）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2E6mnBf%EF%BF%BC%C2%A0%EF%BC%89&d=6XWd9CfFHb3CQP82H0cbYFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=053ed9cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2E6mnBf￼&nbsp;）</a><br />\n<br />\n不過，基斯唔演唔等於美國隊長已死，早前美國一名8歲小朋友AJ，因腦內有多達8個無辦法做手術清除嘅瘤而受病魔折磨，基斯知道AJ好鍾意美國隊長之後，即刻拍片同AJ對話：「Hey！AJ，美國隊長來了，聽說你很喜歡超級英雄及美國隊長，所以很明顯地你是個聰明的小子，這是天賦。」<br />\n之後基斯再講道：「我剛剛看完你的情況，聽起來我認為你是我聽說過最強大最勇敢的孩子，我不知道你從哪來的勇氣，對我來說，你就是超級英雄，我在電影中演繹而你卻是現實中真正的超級英雄。」<br />\n基斯仲話：「你對我有很大的啟發，你的勇氣、你的堅韌，會給予像我一樣的人及你身邊的人鼓舞，所以謝謝你，我非常興幸可以知道你的事，我會一直記住你及為你祈禱，所以你要撐住啊老兄。」<br />\n<br />\n而AJ喺收到基斯嘅片段之後都有拍片回敬，仲揹住佢最鍾意嘅美國隊長背囊，AJ更分享佢喺醫院嘅趣事：「我們都可以為自己的地方命名，我的叫做Steve Rogers（美國隊長角色名字）就像你！」<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://goo.gl/7hQbXU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F7hQbXU&d=6XWd9CfFHb3CQP82H0cbYFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=d548c421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/7hQbXU</a><br />\n<br />\nMarvel既公關機器永遠都唔會停落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2931e9e0e93da5b52857994f170723cd917afba5","tid":854519,"uid":205498,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"公你老母"},{"pid":"c8bb95999b4c34d85c785a24e8ffe8d7264a170f","tid":854519,"uid":170044,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"其實想問下點解好多巨星拍到出晒名之後又話唔再演<br />\n係因為賺夠定真係想抽離個角色？"},{"pid":"ace503bed1fff27aff220ad7b9abc52cf6bef6eb","tid":854519,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6fd2e0206b3050107ce349cdac00d9fe90ec905b","tid":854519,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181009/large/1539081541_02a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F1539081541_02a0.jpg&h=f925cb5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\